keyMappings:
# Insert your preferred key mappings here.
unmap g$
unmap gT
unmap gt
unmap yf
unmap b
unmap <f8>
unmap <a-p>
unmap <a-s-c>
unmap <a-c>
unmap <a-t>
unmap zH
unmap zL
map P togglePinTab
map t createTab
map cr closeTabsOnRight
map cl closeTabsOnLeft
map ca closeOtherTabs
map g9 lastTab
map af LinkHints.activateFocus
map z. scrollToRight
map z, scrollToLeft
map K goForward
map J goBack
map H previousTab
map L nextTab
map yl LinkHints.activateModeToCopyLinkUrl
searchEngines:
w: https://www.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Special:Search&search=%s Wikipedia
g: https://www.google.com/search?q=%s Google
b: https://www.bing.com/search?q=%s Bing
y: https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=%s Youtube
